title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Siliguri · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 bath
listing_description:
Welcome to our luxurious guest house, conveniently located just 7 minutes away from NJP railway station. We are thrilled to offer you a private room that boasts modern interior design and is equipped with all the amenities you require for a comfortable stay.

You will have access to high-speed wifi, and you will also have access to our sharing living and dining space. Additionally, a personal host will be available.

We look forward to hosting you


Warm regards
Nirajeeta Chowdhury
